" ideavim配置
" 参考1 https://www.jianshu.com/p/ec6b4b4536aa
" 参考2 https://my.oschina.net/funcy/blog/1832719

" Vim 的默认寄存器和系统剪贴板共享
set clipboard+=unnamed
set history=100000

" 突出显示当前行
set cursorline
" 突出显示当前列
set cursorcolumn

" 显示行号
set number

"相对行号
set relativenumber

"用jj取代ESC键
inoremap jj <ESC>

"跳转最后一行
nnoremap <CR> G
"跳转首行
nnoremap <BS> gg

" Tab operation
nnoremap t gt
nnoremap T gT
